{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-arrays-and-loops/learn-arrays-and-loops-lesson-h","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"top-learn-arrays-and-loops","challengeType":15,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Još jedna važna metoda za red podataka je metoda <code>filter()</code>. Metoda <code>filter()</code> kreira novi red sa svim elementima koji prolaze validaciju koju je izvršila navedena funkcija. Sintaksa metode <code>filter()</code> je sledeća:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">const numbers = [2, 5, 6, 1, 9, -1]\n\nconst newNumbers = numbers.filter((number) => {\n  return number > 2;\n});\n\nconsole.log(newNumbers); // Output: [5, 6, 9]\n</code></pre>\n<p>Metoda <code>filter()</code> kreira novi red sa svim elementima većim od 2. Metoda <code>filter()</code> ne menja prvobitni red podataka.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Odin","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-arrays-and-loops/learn-arrays-and-loops-lesson-h"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Šta će biti rezultat ovog fragmenta koda JavaScript ispod?</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">const strings = ['apple', 'banana', 'cherry', 'orange', 'kiwi', 'mango'];\nconst newStrings = strings.filter((string) => {\n  return string.length > 5;\n});\n\nconsole.log(newStrings);\n</code></pre>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><code>['apple', 'banana', 'cherry', 'orange', 'kiwi', 'mango']</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>['apple', 'banana', 'cherry', 'orange', 'kiwi']</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>['banana, 'cherry', 'orange']</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>['banana', 'cherry', 'orange', 'kiwi', 'mango' ]</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"the-odin-pr